feedback_ui_template.message:
1- Please describe the problem you encountered.
2- Did the issue occur while trying to open a file, or while trying to edit a file?
3- Does this issue occur anytime you try to open or edit any files, or just with specific files?

If this issue is specific to a file, please feel free to attach that file to this report, as it will be very helpful in allowing us to troubleshoot the issue more thoroughly.
